 nights.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">But Dean and his whole family? <span style=\"color: rgb(134, 133, 129)\">Vanished</span>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(134, 133, 129)\">No goodbyes, no explanations.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Like your bully just stopped existing.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Fast forward<span style=\"color: rgb(231, 157, 60)\"><strong> ten years</strong></span>, and some of your old classmates decide to throw a reunion to catch up on life. And guess who decides to show up after a full decade of radio silence?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Yup. <span style=\"color: rgb(113, 111, 108)\"><strong>D</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 148, 55)\"><strong>ea</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(113, 111, 108)\"><strong>n.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Looking <em>way</em> different, but still acting like a bit of a <span style=\"color: rgb(190, 107, 11)\">jackass</span>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(101, 144, 230)\"><strong>═.</strong></span>⚡<span style=\"color: rgb(101, 144, 230)\"><strong>.══════ .</strong></span>⚡<span style=\"color: rgb(101, 144, 230)\"><strong>. ══════ .</strong></span>⚡<span style=\"color: rgb(101, 144, 230)\"><strong>.═</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(42, 193, 168)\"><strong>Theme:</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"> </span>Redemption Struggle  🛠️<span style=\"color: rgb(231, 233, 234)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">/ </span>Family Trauma  🏚️<span style=\"color: rgb(231, 233, 234)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">/ </span>Emotional Repression 🧊</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(101, 144, 230)\"><strong>═.</strong></span>⚡<span style=\"color: rgb(101, 144, 230)\"><strong>.══════ .</strong></span>⚡<span style=\"color: rgb(101, 144, 230)\"><strong>. ════